alley-dandelions.jpg 1200w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18113658/interlakken-valley-dandelions-198x300.jpg 198w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18113658/interlakken-valley-dandelions-677x1024.jpg 677w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18113658/interlakken-valley-dandelions-768x1161.jpg 768w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18113658/interlakken-valley-dandelions-1016x1536.jpg 1016w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 786px) 100vw, 786px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e  \u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18112309/interlakken-swiss-flag.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"791\" height=\"1125\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://centsationalstyle.com/2025/05/spring-in-switzerland/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Spring in Switzerland\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18112309/interlakken-swiss-flag.jpg\" srcset=\"https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18112309/interlakken-swiss-flag.jpg 1200w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18112309/interlakken-swiss-flag-211x300.jpg 211w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18112309/interlakken-swiss-flag-720x1024.jpg 720w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18112309/interlakken-swiss-flag-768x1092.jpg 768w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18112309/interlakken-swiss-flag-1080x1536.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 791px) 100vw, 791px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18112919/interlakken-kate-flower.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"779\" height=\"976\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://centsationalstyle.com/2025/05/spring-in-switzerland/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Spring in Switzerland\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18112919/interlakken-kate-flower.jpg\" srcset=\"https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18112919/interlakken-kate-flower.jpg 1200w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18112919/interlakken-kate-flower-239x300.jpg 239w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18112919/interlakken-kate-flower-817x1024.jpg 817w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18112919/interlakken-kate-flower-768x963.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 779px) 100vw, 779px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18113447/interlakken-sunset.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"794\" height=\"755\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://centsationalstyle.com/2025/05/spring-in-switzerland/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Spring in Switzerland\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18113447/interlakken-sunset.jpg\" srcset=\"https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18113447/interlakken-sunset.jpg 1200w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18113447/interlakken-sunset-300x285.jpg 300w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18113447/interlakken-sunset-1024x974.jpg 1024w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18113447/interlakken-sunset-768x730.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 794px) 100vw, 794px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFrom Interlakken we took another scenic train to Lugano where you can feel the shift from German influence to Italian. We ate pizza and drank Italian wine on the shores of Lake Lugano. Did you know it’s so easy to get to the lake region of Italy from Lugano? We hopped a bus that in an hour took us across the border to the town of Menaggio where we then took a ferry and were on Lake Como arriving in Bellagio the very next hour. Bellisimo! I’ll save that 48 hour adventure for a separate post.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOur last part of the loop around Switzerland took us from Lugano to Lucerne. I highly recommend the Gothard Panorama Express train ride, it takes you on a glass domed train from Lugano through the southern part of the country to the edge of Lake Lucerne where you then catch the leisurely 2 hour ferry across the lake to the heart of the town of Lucerne. This was the final highlight of the trip where we enjoyed a beautiful lunch served in front of huge picture windows as the chateaus and castles on the shore drifted by. Stunning!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18114237/gothard-express-kate.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"789\" height=\"953\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://centsationalstyle.com/2025/05/spring-in-switzerland/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Spring in Switzerland\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18114237/gothard-express-kate.jpg\" srcset=\"https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18114237/gothard-express-kate.jpg 1200w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18114237/gothard-express-kate-248x300.jpg 248w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18114237/gothard-express-kate-847x1024.jpg 847w, https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18114237/gothard-express-kate-768x928.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 789px) 100vw, 789px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://media.centsationalstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/18114303/lake-lucerne-ferry-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"7